sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Auth
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as Database/PVC
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>80/443 mTLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Event
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, PVC<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>TrustyAI: Deploy TrustyAI Service
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Initialize Storage<br/>JDBC TLS (optional) / Filesystem
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over KServe,Prometheus: Flow 2: Inference Monitoring
        KServe->>TrustyAI: Send Inference Data<br/>HTTP/HTTPS mTLS (Istio)
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Store Inference Data<br/>JDBC/Filesystem
        Prometheus->>TrustyAI: Scrape Metrics<br/>GET /q/metrics
        TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Fairness/Drift Metrics
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,HF: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Event
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job (via Kueue)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        activate Operator
        Note over Operator: LMEvalJob Pod starts
        Operator->>HF: Download Model/Dataset<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+ (API Token)
        Operator->>KServe: Query Model<br/>gRPC/HTTP TLS
        KServe-->>Operator: Inference Results
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update LMEvalJob Status
        deactivate Operator
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 255)
        Note over User,KServe: Flow 4: Guardrails Orchestration
        User->>K8sAPI: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Event
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>Inject Guardrails
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Guardrails Deployment
        Note over Operator: Client requests route through Guardrails
        KServe->>Operator: Inference Request<br/>HTTPS mTLS (Istio)
        Operator->>KServe: Forward to Detector Services<br/>mTLS
        Operator->>KServe: Forward to LLM Service<br/>mTLS
        KServe-->>Operator: Inference Response
    end
